變相陷入三毛最想見到嘅分化局面"},{"pid":"2367448d495a3b419d4ba175a9cd548e0f096916","tid":1216874,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:35:33.000Z","msg":"如果唔出第時連精都出唔到！"},{"pid":"8d40039542a5930e377778f2dff239a75ab486ab","tid":1216874,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:40:35.000Z","msg":"和理非遊行指在集氣，點都要去"},{"pid":"eeeec0fa6d4a01ac06cad498f797e923f2bec6e8","tid":1216874,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:43:51.000Z","msg":"連續兩星期百萬人遊行，係史上從未見過，和理非既終極武器<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216635/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216635/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"90784b789c6eceb9b6257d8d3e4dcb18b039b161","tid":1216874,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f3f1326423324f44b54df42e1f92f81cb6ca48","tid":1216874,"uid":7855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:44:46.000Z","msg":"減肥一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3c5101669ad6835a85eb1a5405536b4c03f5a8","tid":1216874,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"有平時政治冷感既朋友都話上次103唔係一分子 今次會去參與"}]}